{"tid":1212563,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"音樂戰略行得通？","createTime":"2019-06-12T19:35:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T20:32:20.000Z","uid":256433,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"adf1a3919805b64fc5f590229999fd26c1b8279a","tid":1212563,"uid":256433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:35:42.000Z","msg":"預咗負皮同埋比人話On9，但眼見佢哋有催淚彈又布袋槍又有盾，我哋民眾就咩都冇剩。<br />\n<br />\n見最近有人發起唱聖詩行動，我突然之間喺度諗，利用音樂方式對抗work唔work？咁你表達訴求同埋遊行冇話唔俾用音樂方式進行㗎嘛？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>1.擺設大型音響e.g大聲公丶喇叭 面向黑警<br />\n2.播放高頻率 音樂（e.g海豚音）<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hxP9xTxM1nM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhxP9xTxM1nM&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMa0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=a2e4c254\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hxP9xTxM1nM</a><br />\n<br />\n目的：造成對方精神丶心理及聽覺上疲勞？</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n萬一有咩事起上嚟起碼都有啲喇叭擋住先，起碼呢個方法唔會傷人同埋流血先。<br />\n<br />\n最大問題就係邊度整啲器材返嚟同埋邊度有電源供應<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位巴打絲打你哋點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>今日香港人辛苦了。香港加油！</strong>"},{"pid":"c2eceb6f556399fab155828acec1e0a1bdf58e8b","tid":1212563,"uid":245484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:39:57.000Z","msg":"你有冇諗過自己友都聽緊..?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁大部野有事點走？ 比狗衝一次就成set 冇左啦"},{"pid":"022a38e92a22c826661035e7b12a0f6c245b1bb9","tid":1212563,"uid":44488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:40:27.000Z","msg":"多人企係黑警邊念大悲咒"},{"pid":"a7c958f68f420052e218b41fd4e14c02cb4ab9d7","tid":1212563,"uid":259755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T20:32:20.000Z","msg":"咁不如大家唱 &ldquo;Do you hear the people sing?&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TvR3yw6bni8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTvR3yw6bni8&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMa0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=477c6